{"tid":1862614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子聲稱來自武漢嚇退防暴","createTime":"2020-02-04T17:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:42:24.000Z","uid":299468,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"89bca6c85c67163bbad5fb39f34c58739b6e66e5","tid":1862614,"uid":299468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"【0205 天水圍即時｜「我都是武漢的！」】<br />\n<br />\n0017 一名操普通話的女士對警方突然噴射胡椒噴霧表示不滿，指自己「只是在這裏走」。期間，她大聲向警方稱自己來自武漢，表示希望能傳染肺炎予警方。旁邊記者聞訊嘩然，立即向後退開。及後，該女士除下口罩面向警方咳嗽，警方防線一度後退。<br />\n<br />\n該名女士向記者稱自己數年前來到香港。警方亦向她表示:「得喇得喇，你贏。快啲返屋企喇。」<br />\n<br />\n攝／Chin Wa<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3556746567685865/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3556746567685865%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3YkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=cbd7ead3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3556746567685865/</a>"},{"pid":"24b810b4ca2b938845202caaa4bdcde35bc27dd5","tid":1862614,"uid":255040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"打少陣飛機啦<br />\n咁少事就扯曬旗點做大事"},{"pid":"3d38ae1721d12f7c6eaa55f2c4f25b68cf68a4ff","tid":1862614,"uid":736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n部分鄉音新移民落到嚟反而會屌大陸同屌狗<br />\n呢啲先係願意擁抱香港價值嘅新移民<br />\n反而有啲日日話支那點好嘅廢老又唔敢上去住"},{"pid":"bf68484e381b278d50be8f32e203dc8c280000bf","tid":1862614,"uid":254547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:23:54.000Z","msg":"警方亦向她表示:「<span style=\"color: red;\">得喇得喇，你贏。</span>快啲返屋企喇。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1100066e43b4458dc1e748b220d81afaed5ac8f","tid":1862614,"uid":36049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"班狗縮到<img src=\"/assets/f